    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I remembered how to do this really quickly. You have to go to File -&gt; Project Structure. Then click the Libraries tab and the green plus. Once clicked select from Maven and then search GSON and find the correct GSON version you want to use from the menu and then GSON dependency will work.</p>\n"
